OL,3,CLaser clinic fined for data breach and
OL,4,Cthreats to former worker
OL,6,FA Jersey laser clinic has been charged
OL,7,F#500 after inappropriately sharing
OL,8,Finformation about an employee who had
OL,9,Fresigned.
OL,11,FAn unnamed director at JRSY Laser
OL,12,FLimited, based in St Helier, informed
OL,13,Fother members of staff via email about
OL,14,Fthe reasons why the worker had left
OL,15,Fand details of a dispute.
OL,17,FThe director made "insulting comments"
OL,18,Fin this message and also threatened to
OL,19,Fshare the employee's personal
OL,20,Finformation with a third party.
