OL,3,CLaser clinic fined for data breach and
OL,4,Cthreats to former worker
OL,6,FThe former worker says they felt
OL,7,F"threatened, embarrassed and hurt by
OL,8,Fthe content of the email shared with
OL,9,Fthe JRSY Laser staff" and was left
OL,10,Fwith "emotional distress, anxiety and
OL,11,Flow self-esteem".
OL,13,FThe regulator says JRSY Laser believed
OL,14,Fit was appropriate to share the email
OL,15,Fwith other members of staff as they
OL,16,Fconsidered the team a "family" and the
OL,17,Fdirector felt the rest of the workers
OL,18,Fhad a right to know.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
