OL,3,CLaser clinic fined for data breach and
OL,4,Cthreats to former worker
OL,6,FHowever, the Authority concluded that
OL,7,Fwhilst sharing information about the
OL,8,Femployee leaving was acceptable,
OL,9,F"there was no reason to share any
OL,10,Fother information about their
OL,11,Fdeparture and circumstances
OL,12,Fsurrounding it".
OL,14,FThe regulator added: "This was
OL,15,Fexcessive and there was no lawful
OL,16,Fbasis (legitimate reason) for doing
OL,17,Fthis."
