OL,3,CLaser clinic fined for data breach and
OL,4,Cthreats to former worker
OL,6,FDuring the investigation, it also came
OL,7,Fto light that JRSY Laser had not
OL,8,Fcomplied with certain aspects of the
OL,9,FData Protection Jersey Law 2018.
OL,11,FFollowing the company's "almost
OL,12,Fidentical" complaint in 2023, the
OL,13,Fregulator summarised that JRSY Laser
OL,14,F"still showed a general lack of
OL,15,Fcompliance and understanding of their
OL,16,Fobligations under the Law".
OL,18,FIn a victim statement, the affected
OL,19,Femployee "outlined the very real
OL,20,Fdistress that had been caused by
OL,21,FDirector A's actions".
