OL,6,F"The Authority wishes to stress that
OL,7,Fwhen an organisation has already been
OL,8,Fsubject of an investigation, orders
OL,9,Fand a Public Statement issued, if that
OL,10,Forganisation then repeats that
OL,11,Fbehaviour (indicating that lessons
OL,12,Fhave not been learnt), the Authority
OL,13,Fwill not hesitate to increase the
OL,14,Fseverity of its sanction, including
OL,15,Fissuing a fine if appropriate.
